    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i've also been eating really healthy and exercising way more lately. i read online that if your lifestyle is dialed in you don't need as much chemical help to keep things steady. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg be a more reasonable baseline for someone who is actually taking care of themselves? it just feels like i'm overmedicating now.",
